program.name: HFS Family Planning Program
program.description: The HFS Family Planning Program provides family planning services to eligible individuals who are not currently enrolled in Medicaid or other comprehensive health coverage. Services include contraception, family planning counseling, STI testing, and related care.
program.website_description: Reproductive health and family planning related services

documents.text: Proof of Illinois residency (ex: lease, utility bill, state ID)
Proof of identity (ex: driver's license, state ID)
Proof of individual income (ex: pay stubs, employer letter)
Proof of status in U.S. (ex: birth certificate, green card, work permit)
